in-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/193258/', '', 'Artesunate, Mefloquine, Lumefantrine, Artemether, Pyrimethamine, Atovaquone, Hydroxychloroquine, Halofantrine, Proguanil, Sulfadoxine', 'Zinc sulfate, Diltiazem, Zinc acetate, Fluocinolone acetonide, Hydrocortisone, Fluocinonide, Isosorbide dinitrate, Zinc chloride, Prednisolone, Betamethasone, Fluorometholone, More', 1767369485);
